AliceTLG =["How nice it would be if we could only get through into Looking-glass House! I'm sure it's got, oh! such beautiful things in it!", "Oh, what fun it'll be, when they see me through the glass in here, and can't get at me!","Somehow it seems to fill my head with ideas—only I don't exactly know what they are!","How is it you can all talk so nicely? I've been in many gardens before, but none of the flowers could talk.","It's a great huge game of chess that's being played—all over the world—if this is the world at all, you know. Oh, what fun it is! How I wish I was one of them! I wouldn't mind being a Pawn, if only I might join—though of course I should like to be a Queen, best.","I know I should have to get through the Looking-glass again – back into the old room – and there'd be an end of all my adventures!","Tweedledum and Tweedledee agreed to have a battle; For Tweedledum said Tweedledee had spoiled his nice new rattle. Just then flew down a monstrous crow, as black as a tar-barrel; Which frightened both the heroes so, they quite forgot their quarrel.","Humpty Dumpty sat on a wall: Humpty Dumpty had a great fall. All the King's horses and all the King's men Couldn't put Humpty Dumpty in his place again."]

